author: julianfoad
msg: On the 'move-tracking-2' branch: More WC behaviour for svnmover:
introduce a separate 'commit' command and don't commit automatically
after each line of input in the interactive mode.
wc_create): Track whether we made changes to the WC.
commit_callback): Report the new committed revision.
(execute): Don't 'check out' the WC here. Commit it on specific command
but not automatically on exit. Do not destroy the WC object.
(sub_main): 'Check out' a WC before the interactive command loop, and
